data.description: This charming cottage boasts a prime central location of Bear Lake Reserve. Surrounded by tranquility, the property features sounds of a nearby babbling creek, offering serene days and evenings. Inside, exquisite hardwood floors and vaulted ceilings adorn the spacious living room and kitchen, creating an inviting space for gatherings. A cozy stacked stone gas fireplace adds to the mountain ambiance. The main floor encompasses a generous primary suite, a delightful guest bedroom, and a well-appointed bathroom. Step onto the screened-in porch, complete with a wood-burning fireplace, ideal for enjoying the outdoors year-round. Descend to the lower level, where a sizable family room, laundry facilities, and another bedroom and bathroom await. A second porch on this level extends the living space outdoors. Fully furnished and equipped, this home is poised for comfortable living and entertaining, allowing family and guests to indulge in the array of amenities provided by Bear Lake Reserve.
